Package com.paymill.services

Class Summary
ClientService The ClientService is used to list, create, edit, delete and update PAYMILL Clients.
OfferService The OfferService is used to list, create, edit, delete and update PAYMILL Offers.
PaymentService The PaymentService is used to list, create, edit, delete and update PAYMILL Payments.
PreauthorizationService The PreauthorizationService is used to list, create and delete PAYMILL Preauthorizations.
RefundService The RefundService is used to list and create PAYMILL Refunds.
SubscriptionService The SubscriptionService is used to list, create, edit, delete and update PAYMILL Subscriptions.
TransactionService The TransactionService is used to list, create, edit and update PAYMILL Transactions.
WebhookService The WebhookService is used to list, create, edit and update PAYMILL Webhooks.
